        "text": "A1 Basketball star Shanille O'Keal's team statistician keeps track of the number, S(N), of successful free throws she has made in her fi rst N attempts of the sea- son. Early in the season, S(N) was less than 80% of N, but by the end of the season, S(N) was more than 80% of N. Was there necessarily a moment in between when S(N) was exactly 80% of N?",
